{"data":{"page":{"id":"bf2f524f-bba8-5023-b8c7-d9fc73c204fe","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/89dfbdbd31333468c14fd7096dd5ad27/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/89dfbdbd31333468c14fd7096dd5ad27/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89dfbdbd31333468c14fd7096dd5ad27/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/89dfbdbd31333468c14fd7096dd5ad27/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>While working at Webmarket, <a href=\"http://www.seor.es/\">SEOR</a> (Sociedad Española de Oncología Radioterápica) contacted me to request for a custom interactive application development and a video recording service of a few their convections in Navarra, Spain.</p>\n<p>The application consisted of a Flash video player with categories and synchronized powerpoint presentations. The slides would automatically change based on the video’s current position.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/69fa32b5e17a17facc4d3a195bd24667/54137/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1002px; margin-